        "body": "<p>You can use something like this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String query = \"Query\";\nint result = statement.executeUpdate(query);\nSystem.out.println(result);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>If result is 0 , no updates, insert, delete was executed (no rows affected) but if you get > 0 then the number returned is the number of row affected <\/p>\n",
